Package: mbrglm
Type: Package
Title: Median bias reduction in Binomial-response GLMs
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2016-09-07
Author: Euloge Clovis Kenne Pagui, Nicola Sartori  and Alessandra Salvan 
Maintainer: Euloge C. Kenne Pagui <kenne@stat.unipd.it>
Description: Fit generalized linear models with binomial responses using  a median modified score approach to median bias reduction. This method respects equivariance under reparameterizations for each parameter component and also solves the infinite estimates problem (data separation).
License: GPL-2
Suggests: brglm
Depends: R (>= 2.6.0), nleqslv, enrichwith